FBIS3-9948 "drlat039_m_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 Brazil Government Condemns Killing of Palestinians in Hebron PY2602173494 Madrid EFE in Spanish 2359 GMT 25 Feb 94 PY2602173494 Madrid EFE Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Brasilia, 25 Feb (EFE) -- In an official note, the Brazilian Government demanded today that Israel speed up the peace process with the Palestinians in repudiating the killing of dozens of Palestinians by an Israeli settler in a Hebron mosque. The Brazilian Foreign Ministry expressed "its indignation and strong condemnation of that act" and called on Israel "to adopt the necessary measures to prevent new violence from occurring" in the region.
